reviewText: Great show, this is a collector's item because it's generally high priced due to production being cut early. Definitely worth having though, awesome show!
Absolutely Great show, Absolutely unreasonable price for a DVD Complete collection or Single disc. I know there's the rarity factor  but anyone who would pay that price is a sucker.
The individual cases come with a different Beck: MCS guitar pick in each dvd case, great for the avid fan.
A friend of mine requested this for Christmas. Have not watched the series myself, but she said she really loves it.
This item was pretty much delivered instantly, it beat the rest of the collection by a week, it was in brand new condishion like posted and everything inside still there, thank you very much
